Clusters can be imported using project ID and cluster name, in the format `PROJECTID-CLUSTERNAME`, e.g.

```sh
 $ pulumi import mongodbatlas:index/cluster:Cluster my_cluster 1112222b3bf99403840e8934-Cluster0
```

